graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Notebook Controller"
        Controller[OpenshiftNotebookReconciler<br/>Controller]
        Webhook[NotebookWebhook<br/>Mutating Webhook]
        HTTPRouteMgr[HTTPRoute Manager]
        ReferenceGrantMgr[ReferenceGrant Manager]
        NetworkPolicyMgr[NetworkPolicy Manager]
        RBACMgr[RBAC Manager]
        ProxyConfigGen[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Config Generator]
        DSPAIntegration[DSPA Integration]

        Controller -->|manages| HTTPRouteMgr
        Controller -->|manages| ReferenceGrantMgr
        Controller -->|manages| NetworkPolicyMgr
        Controller -->|manages| RBACMgr
        Controller -->|manages| ProxyConfigGen
        Controller -->|manages| DSPAIntegration
    end

    User[User] -->|creates| NotebookCR[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    NotebookCR -->|watched by| Controller
    NotebookCR -->|mutated by| Webhook

    Webhook -->|injects when<br/>inject-auth=true| KubeRBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>sidecar]

    Controller -->|creates| HTTPRoute[HTTPRoute<br/>gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1]
    Controller -->|creates| ReferenceGrant[ReferenceGrant<br/>gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1beta1]
    Controller -->|creates| NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy<br/>networking.k8s.io/v1]
    Controller -->|creates| ServiceAccount[ServiceAccount]
    Controller -->|creates| Role[Role]
    Controller -->|creates| RoleBinding[RoleBinding]
    Controller -->|creates| ConfigMap[ConfigMap]
    Controller -->|creates| Secret[Secret<br/>Pipeline Token]

    HTTPRoute -->|references| Gateway[Gateway<br/>data-science-gateway]
    HTTPRoute -->|routes to| NotebookService[Notebook Service<br/>8888/TCP]

    Controller -->|depends on| KubeflowController[Kubeflow Notebook<br/>Controller]
    Controller -->|depends on| GatewayAPI[Gateway API<br/>v1.2.1]
    Controller -->|depends on| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA<br/>Operator]

    Controller -->|integrates with| DSPOperator[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Operator]
    Controller -->|integrates with| DSGateway[Data Science Gateway]
    Controller -->|integrates with| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2
    style HTTPRouteMgr fill:#4a90e2
    style ReferenceGrantMgr fill:#4a90e2
    style NetworkPolicyMgr fill:#4a90e2
    style RBACMgr fill:#4a90e2
    style ProxyConfigGen fill:#4a90e2
    style DSPAIntegration fill:#4a90e2
    style NotebookCR fill:#f5a623
    style HTTPRoute fill:#f5a623
    style ReferenceGrant fill:#f5a623
    style KubeflowController fill:#999
    style GatewayAPI fill:#999
    style ServiceCA fill:#999
    style DSPOperator fill:#7ed321
    style DSGateway fill:#7ed321
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321
